fields.calculatedFormula:
HYPERLINK(
"https://www.autoidinc.com/recovery/passThru/salesforce/"&
CASE(Evaluator_AID__c, "NADA", "nada?", "Black Book", "bb?", "kbb?")&
"recovery=true&"&
"mileage="&TEXT(Mileage_AID__c)&"&"&
"vin="&VIN__c&"&"&
"date="&TEXT(MONTH(Request_Date_AID__c))&"/"&TEXT(DAY(Request_Date_AID__c))&"/"&TEXT(YEAR(Request_Date_AID__c))&"&"&
CASE(Evaluator_AID__c, 
"NADA", "cpo="&IF(ISPICKVAL(NADA_CPO_AID__c, "Yes"), "true", "false")&"&"&"edition="&Edition_Region_URL__c,
"Black Book", "withResiduals="&IF(ISPICKVAL(BB_Residual_AID__c, "Yes"), "true", "false")&"&"&"region="&Edition_Region_URL__c&"&"&"frequency="&TEXT(BB_Frequency_AID__c),
 "region="&Edition_Region_AID__c)&"&"&
"loanId="& CASESAFEID(Id )
,
 'Click Here')

fields.calculatedFormula:
MOD(value(

      (left(right(text(CreatedDate),6),2))&     

      text(DAY(DATEVALUE(CreatedDate)))&

      text(Month(DATEVALUE(CreatedDate)))&

      text(Year(DATEVALUE(CreatedDate)))&

      (left(right(text(CreatedDate),9),2))

)
*
value( Year_AID__c )
*
 Evaluator_Value_AID__c,  Total_Discrepancy_Amount__c )

fields.name: Random__c

fields.calculatedFormula:
(TODAY() - Latest_First_Mailing_Date__c >= Terms__r.Mailing_Interval_1st_to_2nd__c) 
&& (ISBLANK(Second_Mailing_Date__c) || Latest_Second_Mailing_Date__c < Latest_First_Mailing_Date__c) 
&& ISPICKVAL(Status__c, "Mailed") 
&& NOT(ISBLANK(Lender__r.Cover_Letter_Template_2__c)) 
&& Open_Balance__c >=Lender__r.Open_Balance_Mailing_Threshold__c
fields.label: Second Mailing Ready
fields.name: Second_Mailing_Ready__c

fields.calculatedFormula:
(TODAY() - Latest_Second_Mailing_Date__c >= Terms__r.Mailing_Interval_2nd_to_3rd__c) 
&& Latest_Second_Mailing_Date__c > Latest_First_Mailing_Date__c 
&& (ISBLANK(Third_Mailing_Date__c) || Latest_Third_Mailing_Date__c < Latest_Second_Mailing_Date__c) 
&& ISPICKVAL(Status__c, "Mailed") 
&& NOT(ISBLANK(Lender__r.Cover_Letter_Template_3__c)) 
&& Open_Balance__c >=Lender__r.Open_Balance_Mailing_Threshold__c
fields.label: Third Mailing Ready
fields.name: Third_Mailing_Ready__c

fields.calculatedFormula:
if(ISPICKVAL(Status__c, "Processed")|| 
ISPICKVAL(Status__c, "Mail Batched") ||
ISPICKVAL(Status__c, "Mailed") ||
ISPICKVAL(Status__c, "Paid in Full") ||
ISPICKVAL(Status__c, "Closed"),
Bookout_Value__c-Evaluator_Value_AID__c- Total_Discrepancy_Adjustment__c, 
0)
